    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

    <div class="part text ">

        <p><h2>Real-time email address validation</h2></p>

        <p>Email validation is one of our leading service which allows you to make sure your email data base is up to date and all your emails will be delivert corectly!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="">
