        <ul>
            <li>Cleansing your email data base</li>
            <li>API integration</li>
            <li>Shopping cart solutions API integration </li>
            <li>Marketing</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p>Email validation service can be installed and integrated in minutes.</p>



    <h3 style="color:#22445B; margin-top:30px;">Email validation examples</h3>
    <div class="row">

        <div class="text-center">

            <h2 class="blue">Example with table integration</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="example">
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                Email validation showing resultas as table. Easy and fast for integration on any platform.
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <form id="search" onsubmit="return false" class="navbar-form">
                    <div id="loading" style="display:none">
                        <img src="../../../Content/img/loading-gallery-120.gif" class="loadingEmail" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" id="emailAddr" value="" class="form-control" placeholder="Email address to verify" />
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" id="emailBtn" class="btn btn-success" onclick="getResults(apiNumber)">Check email </button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <table class="table table-striped table-hover" id="emailTable">
                <tr>
                    <th class="col-lg-5">Email address</th>
                    <th class="col-lg-4">Is valid</th>
                    <th class="col-lg-2">Delete</th>
                </tr>
                <tbody></tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

